loli (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package (native). Mirrors the RPM layout: app under
    /usr/share/loli, launcher at /usr/bin/loli, .desktop and scalable icon.
  * Distro is auto-detected at runtime (loli/platform_spec.py); on Debian the
    panel drives apache2, redis-server, apt, a2enmod/a2ensite and per-version
    PHP via update-alternatives.

